name: depth-to-water-in-the-high-plains-aquifer-in-colorado-2000
notes: These data are in support of report DS 456 (Arnold and others, 2009). This grid represents the depth to groundwater in the High Plains Aquifer in Colorado in 2000. The depth-to-water grid was generated for the entire High Plains Aquifer from depth-to-water measurements collected in 2000. Shown as figure 12 in McMahon and others (2007).
